1
00:00:06,010 --> 00:00:08,630
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:12,190
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,190 --> 00:00:18,280
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:24,500
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:31,030
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,030 --> 00:00:36,010
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:43,210
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,210 --> 00:00:48,340
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:49,850
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:55,610
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,610 --> 00:01:02,210
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,210 --> 00:01:08,380
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,380 --> 00:01:11,760
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:27,715
Do you still want to keep fighting?

15
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:34,304
Gao Yang. Gao Yang!

16
00:01:36,219 --> 00:01:37,779
I'm fine.

17
00:01:37,779 --> 00:01:40,360
Do you know why I'm so good to you?

18
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,840
I know, I know.

19
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:44,137
You're repaying my dad's kindness.

20
00:01:44,137 --> 00:01:47,599
Yes, you're Mr. Gao's son.

21
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:49,060
Mr. Gao is my favorite teacher.

22
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:51,380
He was the one who recruited me to the No. 3 High School.

23
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:54,279
He made me into who I am today.

24
00:01:57,499 --> 00:02:00,640
Alright, that's it for today.

25
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,363
Let's go.

26
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:08,552
Take care.

27
00:02:13,471 --> 00:02:15,820
Gao Yang! Gao Yang, are you okay?

28
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:18,299
I'm fine. How bad can it be?

29
00:02:21,659 --> 00:02:23,679
What are you looking at?

30
00:02:26,779 --> 00:02:29,680
We should tell your dad or we won't hear the end of it.

31
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:33,999
Because you were there back then, that's why I didn't fight back, you know? I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

32
00:02:33,999 --> 00:02:37,224
When I'm alone next time, I'll beat him up, okay? Let's go.

33
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:51,172
How did you get out?

34
00:02:51,172 --> 00:02:53,279
I jumped out the window.

35
00:02:53,279 --> 00:02:55,260
Jumped out the window?

36
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,799
You're so great. Come on then.

37
00:02:57,799 --> 00:02:59,460
Let's keep going.

38
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:01,899
You want to fight again? Don't fight.

39
00:03:01,899 --> 00:03:04,219
I'll show you my real skills.

40
00:03:04,219 --> 00:03:05,703
Come on.

41
00:03:10,779 --> 00:03:12,320
You're not going to fight?

42
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,923
Fine then.

43
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:20,180
I won't let you go to Beijing.

44
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,900
Wait, who's going to Beijing?

45
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,900
I'm going to take a shower.

46
00:03:29,059 --> 00:03:31,441
- Are you really okay?
- I'm fine.

47
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:36,140
[Episode 3: Don't Offend My Self-Respect]

48
00:03:41,587 --> 00:03:43,336
Who is that?

49
00:03:43,336 --> 00:03:45,030
Director An's ex-husband.

50
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:47,570
[Meilana Cosmetics]

51
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,939
When can I see Anna? I've been waiting for a long time.

52
00:03:59,939 --> 00:04:03,061
Please wait for a while longer. Director An is in a meeting.

53
00:04:24,219 --> 00:04:26,192
You're looking for Anna too?

54
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:37,460
Judging from your accent, you from Tieyuan, right?

55
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:40,504
I'm from Tieyuan too.

56
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,620
When did you move to Beijing?

57
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:45,420
Move to Beijing for what?

58
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:47,780
I'm still living in Tieyuan.

59
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:49,339
You're Anna's…

60
00:04:49,339 --> 00:04:51,380
I'm her ex-husband.

61
00:04:52,979 --> 00:04:55,579
Pardon me for the disrespect.

62
00:04:55,579 --> 00:04:59,079
Bro, here's my business card.

63
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,779
Don't cotton up with me.

64
00:05:00,779 --> 00:05:02,448
When can I see Anna?

65
00:05:02,448 --> 00:05:03,774
I've really been waiting for a long time.

66
00:05:03,774 --> 00:05:07,579
Sir, please be patient. It'll be soon. Please wait for a bit longer.

67
00:05:07,579 --> 00:05:09,820
I only have a few words. I'll go tell her myself.

68
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:12,679
Sir! Sir, you can't go in there.

69
00:05:12,679 --> 00:05:15,500
Mr. Gao, please don't be anxious.

70
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:18,214
Director Zhan, Director An will see you now.

71
00:05:18,214 --> 00:05:19,999
How come he can go in?

72
00:05:19,999 --> 00:05:23,020
Director An's schedule is already full today. She really has no time.

73
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:25,759
She booked a room at the Kempinski Hotel tonight. Please head over there first.

74
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:29,520
Bro, theoretically, I should let you go first.

75
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:32,820
But I indeed came before you today.

76
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:34,567
I'm sorry.

77
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,179
Wait a minute.

78
00:05:37,179 --> 00:05:40,680
You're sure Anna will go to the Kempinski Hotel, right?

79
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:43,000
- Yes.
- Fine, I'll go there first and wait for her.

80
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:46,720
If she doesn't come, you'll bear the consequences.

81
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,380
Gao Yang, why won't you just admit defeat to Dong Dawei?

82
00:05:57,380 --> 00:06:00,330
Otherwise, you'll have to suffer a beating every day.

83
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:02,599
Be quiet. There's an outsider here.

84
00:06:04,339 --> 00:06:06,430
Let me tell you!

85
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:11,100
Swallow this secret and never spit it out. You're not allowed to tell anyone!

86
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:13,060
Can I tell Beibei? Her dad is the principal.

87
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:14,299
No.

88
00:06:14,299 --> 00:06:16,779
A man must settle his own problems.

89
00:06:16,779 --> 00:06:18,839
Dong Dawei is always bullying you.

90
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,560
What bullying?

91
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,280
It's just a friendly competition.

92
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:24,100
He gained the upper hand this time.

93
00:06:24,100 --> 00:06:27,200
I'll just win it back next time.

94
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:37,899
Sis, are you done?

95
00:06:37,899 --> 00:06:40,380
Why are you carrying so many things?

96
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:43,859
Mom gave us a total of 20 Yuan, ten for each of us.

97
00:06:43,859 --> 00:06:46,348
Go put these useless things back.

98
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:59,140
Niu Wanwan?

99
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:05,019
Your makeup and hairpin are so boorish.

100
00:07:05,019 --> 00:07:06,640
Why should you decide if it's boorish?

101
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,260
I'll buy whatever I want.

102
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,840
It's for your own good.

103
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:12,960
As the President of the Student Union, I think it's my duty to remind you.

104
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,900
Don't bring shame to our No. 3 High School, okay?

105
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:18,000
How am I shaming our No. 3 High School?

106
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,360
Be quiet.

107
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:22,559
I'm only reminding you kindly because you're the principal's daughter.

108
00:07:22,559 --> 00:07:23,859
I don't need it.

109
00:07:23,859 --> 00:07:25,399
Check out, Boss.

110
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:27,500
I want this one.

111
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:30,474
- Twenty Yuan.
- What?

112
00:07:30,474 --> 00:07:32,469
It's that's expensive?

113
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,779
I'll take it.

114
00:07:38,779 --> 00:07:40,639
Don't you know first come, first serve?

115
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,020
Do you have money?

116
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,711
I...

117
00:07:45,779 --> 00:07:48,719
We'll buy it!

118
00:07:48,719 --> 00:07:51,720
What? We have money!

119
00:07:56,099 --> 00:07:58,118
Be boorish then.

120
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:04,700
What are you doing, Doudou? Give it to me.

121
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:08,400
Who said it's for you? I bought it for myself!

122
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:11,260
Why do you need a hairpin?

123
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:25,799
What?

124
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:29,720
I'm not giving it to you.

125
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,660
Aren't you not going to Beijing anymore?

126
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:34,059
How can I take Mi Jia to dinner without money?

127
00:08:34,059 --> 00:08:36,500
Who agreed for you to see her?

128
00:08:38,439 --> 00:08:42,420
About Dong Dawei, how do you plan to solve the problem?

129
00:08:42,420 --> 00:08:45,160
Just let it be. What is there to resolve?

130
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,420
Does getting beat up mean not eating?

131
00:08:47,420 --> 00:08:48,779
Are you giving it to me or not?

132
00:08:48,779 --> 00:08:50,641
No.

133
00:08:50,641 --> 00:08:52,040
Fine, don't give it to me.

134
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,433
I have ways to take Mi Jia to dinner.

135
00:09:04,819 --> 00:09:06,240
Wait, why do you have my phone?

136
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,480
My mom bought it for me.

137
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,919
Hello? Who is it?

138
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:12,260
Are you Ye Xiaowen?

139
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,060
No, you called the wrong number.

140
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:15,280
Don't call randomly next time.

141
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:17,920
I… I'm Mi Jia.

142
00:09:19,010 --> 00:09:22,519
Mi Jia? I'm your Brother Gao, Gao Yang.

143
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,560
Ignore him.

144
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,939
Go on.

145
00:09:26,939 --> 00:09:28,539
There are problems that I can't solve.

146
00:09:28,539 --> 00:09:31,380
Okay, I'll come over now.

147
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:33,220
What is it? I'll go with you.

148
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:36,099
- We'll go eat stew in iron pots together afterwards.
- Stew in iron pots? Bring me along!

149
00:09:36,099 --> 00:09:38,760
Go away. Go home and eat by yourself.

150
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,000
Fine, I'll go home.

151
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:47,679
Xiaowen, can you go home with me to get changed?

152
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:50,635
I want to dress up more handsomely to go see Mi Jia.

153
00:09:57,479 --> 00:10:00,120
Dad, we're home.

154
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,739
- Dad, how was your sleep?
- I didn't sleep.

155
00:10:02,739 --> 00:10:04,607
Why didn't you sleep?

156
00:10:05,779 --> 00:10:08,199
What happened to your face?

157
00:10:08,199 --> 00:10:09,399
My goodness!

158
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:11,620
- It was all because of Gao Yang.
- Gao Yang?

159
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:13,059
What did Gao Yang do?

160
00:10:13,059 --> 00:10:16,178
None of your business. Go back to your room.

161
00:10:16,178 --> 00:10:17,459
Wipe your face.

162
00:10:17,459 --> 00:10:19,557
Got it.

163
00:10:20,939 --> 00:10:22,696
What happened?

164
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:28,200
Bin is such a nuisance for going on a business trip now.

165
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,899
Didn't you ask him to go?

166
00:10:29,899 --> 00:10:31,460
I asked him to go?

167
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:33,240
He pestered me to go.

168
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:36,340
There are so many young employees at school. How will it be his turn?

169
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:38,120
Then why did he go?

170
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:42,840
He said he wants to go to Beijing to see Anna and settle their score.

171
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:45,062
They've been divorced for over ten years, yet he wants to settle the score with Anna now?

172
00:10:45,062 --> 00:10:46,679
It's not that.

173
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:49,319
It's about Gao Yang's train hopping.

174
00:10:49,319 --> 00:10:52,359
He thinks it was Anna's idea.

175
00:10:52,359 --> 00:10:55,699
What? That's because the boy doesn't want to live with him.

176
00:10:55,699 --> 00:10:58,100
He couldn't even handle Gao Yang.

177
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,719
Now, there's Xiaowen too.

178
00:10:59,719 --> 00:11:04,679
I want to see how he gets along with two sons.

179
00:11:06,579 --> 00:11:07,939
What you said is true.

180
00:11:07,939 --> 00:11:09,640
He's been divorced for over ten years.

181
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:12,459
Instead of finding a step-mom for Gao Yang,

182
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:14,579
he brought in Xiaowen.

183
00:11:14,579 --> 00:11:17,360
I want to see how he gets along with that boy.

184
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,419
I'll go make dinner.

185
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:26,020
Do you think Bin and Anna can get back together?

186
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:29,020
No way. She's a big boss now.

187
00:11:29,779 --> 00:11:32,499
That's right. She's a big boss now.

188
00:11:32,499 --> 00:11:34,940
Who will think highly of him?

189
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:40,320
Use this formula for all arithmetic sequences like this.

190
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:44,526
After that, I'll write it in your notebook. Take a look. Can you understand it?

191
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:49,079
Wait, what are you saying?

192
00:11:49,079 --> 00:11:51,419
Mi Jia didn't understand it at all.

193
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:55,500
Why is h-he following us?

194
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,199
Ignore him.

195
00:11:57,199 --> 00:11:58,479
How about this?

196
00:11:58,479 --> 00:12:00,384
I changed it to another method to solve the problem.

197
00:12:00,384 --> 00:12:02,882
Take a look and see if you can understand it.

198
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:08,540
Wait, you... Can you teach her or not?

199
00:12:12,839 --> 00:12:16,024
Mi Jia, if you want to get tutored,

200
00:12:16,024 --> 00:12:19,420
I'll get you a few teachers from our school to teach you privately.

201
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:23,380
The teachers a-a-all listen to you?

202
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:25,059
Of course!

203
00:12:25,059 --> 00:12:28,860
Well, our Grade Leader, Wu Dibao, is at my beck and call.

204
00:12:29,539 --> 00:12:30,860
Call him.

205
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:32,020
Wait, what do you mean?

206
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:34,200
Call him so I can listen in too.

207
00:12:37,579 --> 00:12:39,500
It happens to be dinnertime right now.

208
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:42,039
The teachers are all having dinner. Put that away.

209
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:43,520
Well, let's go get dinner too.

210
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,940
Are you both hungry?

211
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:46,220
I'm not hungry.

212
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:48,220
You're not hungry but Mi Jia is.

213
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:50,198
Am I right, Mi Jia?

214
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,659
See? She's not saying anything so she's agreeing.

215
00:12:52,659 --> 00:12:54,940
- I-I-I…
- Let's go to Stew in Iron Pot!

216
00:12:55,539 --> 00:12:58,179
Zhao Jiabao, is Gao Yang at your place?

217
00:12:58,179 --> 00:12:59,380
Tell him to quickly come home.

218
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:00,900
My dad asked him to come to my place for dinner.

219
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:03,140
Gao Yang has dinner arrangements already. Don't look for him.

220
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:06,659
- He has dinner arrangements. Where?
- Stew in Iron Pot.

221
00:13:06,659 --> 00:13:09,040
You two are eating stew in iron pots without me?

222
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,419
They didn't invite me either.

223
00:13:10,419 --> 00:13:12,779
He said he's treating new classmates to dinner and told me to go home.

224
00:13:12,779 --> 00:13:14,140
What new classmates?

225
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:16,355
Ye Xiaowen

226
00:13:16,355 --> 00:13:18,699
and that pretty new transfer girl.

227
00:13:18,699 --> 00:13:21,060
- Mi Jia!
- That's right.

228
00:13:21,060 --> 00:13:22,480
Zhao Jiabao, get dressed.

229
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,272
I'll see you at Stew in Iron Pot.

230
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:27,880
Where are you going? We're about to have dinner.

231
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,640
To catch Gao Yang.

232
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,300
To catch Gao Yang?

233
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:34,179
Sis, go for it!

234
00:13:34,179 --> 00:13:35,840
Go for it!

235
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,800
What is going on with you?

236
00:14:15,699 --> 00:14:17,408
Waiter, order please.

237
00:14:20,179 --> 00:14:21,800
Hello, Sir.

238
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,910
[Sirloin Steak: 108 Yuan]
[New Land Mutton Steal: 138 Yuan]

239
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:32,660
[Meat Sauce Spaghetti: 68 Yuan]
[Creamy Bacon Torch Macaroni: 78 Yuan]

240
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:38,490
[Garden Vegetable Salad: 48 Yuan]
[Seafood Salad: 68 Yuan]

241
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:54,979
You don't have very little dishes here.

242
00:14:54,979 --> 00:14:56,240
W-We'll talk about it later.

243
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,704
Okay.

244
00:15:01,199 --> 00:15:03,439
Garden Salad, 48.

245
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:06,419
What salad? It's so expensive.

246
00:15:06,419 --> 00:15:08,360
Isn't it just mixed vegetables?

247
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:11,249
Mr. Gao,

248
00:15:12,699 --> 00:15:14,240
why is it you again?

249
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,459
Where's Anna?

250
00:15:15,459 --> 00:15:18,279
Director An has a social engagement tonight. She really can't come.

251
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:20,579
What do you mean? Is she playing with me?

252
00:15:20,579 --> 00:15:21,860
I'll call her now.

253
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:23,900
Mr. Gao, Director An is truly busy.

254
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:25,459
I'm truly sorry.

255
00:15:25,459 --> 00:15:28,459
This is a gift Director An bought for Gao Yang.

256
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:39,860
She thinks she's done her mother's duty by buying him something?

257
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:41,819
Relay my words to Anna.

258
00:15:41,819 --> 00:15:43,539
Tell her not to harass Gao Yang.

259
00:15:43,539 --> 00:15:45,579
Gao Yang is taking the college entrance exam soon.

260
00:15:45,579 --> 00:15:47,740
Don't urge him to come to Beijing anymore.

261
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:02,179
Sir, you forgot your things.

262
00:16:06,699 --> 00:16:08,294
Thank you.

263
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:17,260
Mi Jia, order whatever you want to eat. I'm close with the boss.

264
00:16:17,260 --> 00:16:19,459
Just order whatever.

265
00:16:19,459 --> 00:16:20,740
How can we just order whatever?

266
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:24,040
"Whatever" is what Tieyuan people hate the most.

267
00:16:25,179 --> 00:16:30,600
How about this? Let's first order... a farm-raised chicken, fish, and goose stew. How's that?

268
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:33,900
That's a ten-person portion. How can the three of us finish it?

269
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:35,220
Just take your time eating it then.

270
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:37,220
Mi Jia isn't in a hurry to leave anyway.

271
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:39,240
Am I right, Mi Jia?

272
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:42,759
In a-a bit, I-I'm...

273
00:16:44,959 --> 00:16:46,320
I-I'm leaving in a bit.

274
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:49,099
But what's the hurry, Mi Jia?

275
00:16:56,359 --> 00:16:58,555
Why are you guys here?

276
00:16:58,555 --> 00:17:00,259
Why didn't you invite us if you're treating?

277
00:17:00,259 --> 00:17:01,699
No, no.

278
00:17:01,699 --> 00:17:02,860
Why's that?

279
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:04,880
Our minds are connected and in sync, right?

280
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,819
When it comes to food, even without me telling you, I know you guys will definitely come.

281
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:09,399
Sit down.

282
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:12,720
Xiaowen, let's go.

283
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:19,480
Don't go!

284
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:22,840
What? You're not willing to eat with me?

285
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:30,019
That's not it. Mi Jia still has homework to do.

286
00:17:30,019 --> 00:17:31,606
Perfect.

287
00:17:35,459 --> 00:17:37,152
Do it here.

288
00:17:37,152 --> 00:17:39,640
Beibei, although you do make sense,

289
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:42,459
you should be friendlier to our new classmate.

290
00:17:42,459 --> 00:17:43,900
Shut your mouth!

291
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:45,480
How am I not friendly to her?

292
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:48,280
Aren't I chatting with our new classmates right now? Right, New Classmate?

293
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:52,019
No, Mi… Mi Jia.

294
00:17:52,019 --> 00:17:54,200
Which school did you transfer from?

295
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:56,760
We came from the same school.

296
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,620
Which school is that?

297
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:03,480
- A school out of town.
- Ye Xiaowen, the girls are talking here. Why are you interrupting us?

298
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,619
Come on, Mi Jia. You tell me yourself.

299
00:18:05,619 --> 00:18:07,762
Why did you transfer to our school?

300
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,959
I…

301
00:18:12,419 --> 00:18:15,200
It's time for some fun magic!

302
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:17,219
Yes, we have to do a magic trick before dinner.

303
00:18:17,219 --> 00:18:19,711
Yes, come on, Beibei. Here, blow on it.

304
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:25,419
After Beibei blows on it, the internal structure of this coin will loosen.

305
00:18:25,419 --> 00:18:28,420
After that, it will turn into two coins.

306
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,310
Magic!

307
00:18:33,119 --> 00:18:35,319
Can you not embarrass yourself here?

308
00:18:35,319 --> 00:18:37,920
You even made me feel embarrassed.

309
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,860
You guys don't understand.

310
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,839
How did you do that?

311
00:18:44,979 --> 00:18:47,137
You didn't see it clearly either, right?

312
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:51,100
How did he do that? Let me see yours.

313
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:52,699
I-Is there a m-magnet inside?

314
00:18:52,699 --> 00:18:53,839
Let's try it.

315
00:18:53,839 --> 00:18:55,620
No, there isn't.

316
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:57,459
H-how did he do it then?

317
00:18:57,459 --> 00:18:59,100
I don't know.

318
00:18:59,100 --> 00:19:00,954
It's so magical!

319
00:19:00,954 --> 00:19:03,910
[Li Ji's Stewed Fish in Iron Pot]

320
00:19:03,910 --> 00:19:07,659
Gao Yang, can you do that for us again?

321
00:19:07,659 --> 00:19:11,179
I can only do the same magic trick in front of the same crowd once.

322
00:19:11,179 --> 00:19:13,219
You don't have another chance.

323
00:19:13,219 --> 00:19:15,520
- Well, I need to go to the restroom.
- So stingy.

324
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:17,726
He's going to the restroom again?

325
00:19:18,659 --> 00:19:20,019
By the way, Mi Jia.

326
00:19:20,019 --> 00:19:22,200
I think you're pretty nice. You're not pretentious.

327
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:24,359
You'll admit you didn't understand the magic trick.

328
00:19:24,359 --> 00:19:27,600
I finally found a bosom friend. Let's hang out together.

329
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,879
Sure.

330
00:19:28,879 --> 00:19:32,279
However, I feel like there's one thing wrong with you.

331
00:19:32,279 --> 00:19:33,860
I noticed that it seems like

332
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:37,359
you're not really willing to... Go ahead and eat first.

333
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:43,319
I noticed you don't really like to talk.

334
00:19:43,319 --> 00:19:45,299
What do you think about me?

335
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:54,039
Your hairpin is nice.

336
00:19:58,739 --> 00:19:59,979
Hairpin.

337
00:20:00,079 --> 00:20:03,000
Hairpin? What about the hairpin?

338
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,939
Th-the hairpin looks good.

339
00:20:05,939 --> 00:20:11,040
Really? You think so too? I'll give it to you.

340
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:14,579
It's okay. Take it. It's my gift to you.

341
00:20:14,579 --> 00:20:19,579
Look, I told you. That Niu Wanwan said my hairpin is boorish.

342
00:20:19,579 --> 00:20:22,919
She's just the President of the Student Union. What's so great about her?

343
00:20:22,919 --> 00:20:26,039
Mi Jia, do you know that Niu Wanwan?

344
00:20:26,039 --> 00:20:28,089
What do you think about her?

345
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:34,039
Right? I really hate her. What's your reason?

346
00:20:35,630 --> 00:20:41,619
I-I-I-I-I didn't wear my school uniform to school.

347
00:20:41,619 --> 00:20:45,779
Sh-sh-she recorded it as a d-demerit.

348
00:20:45,779 --> 00:20:47,919
She recorded a demerit for you?

349
00:20:47,919 --> 00:20:53,459
That's outrageous! You just came to the school. Where would you get the uniform?

350
00:20:53,459 --> 00:20:58,599
Here's what you do, Mi Jia. If she bullies you again in the future, just tell me. I'm not afraid of her.

351
00:20:58,599 --> 00:20:59,900
Who is being bullied?

352
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:02,499
Niu Wanwan bullied Mi Jia.

353
00:21:06,930 --> 00:21:09,510
- You want to stand up for her?
- Yes.

354
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:11,990
Do you know who Niu Wanwan is?

355
00:21:12,939 --> 00:21:16,950
If what you just said gets out, let me tell you, even I can't save you.

356
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:19,660
Do you know who's the person backing her?

357
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:22,680
Who?

358
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:26,700
- Who?
- Who?

359
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:28,680
Dong Dawei.

360
00:21:29,739 --> 00:21:32,800
Do you know what kind of person Dong Dawei is?

361
00:21:35,259 --> 00:21:38,079
A giant hillbilly!

362
00:21:43,970 --> 00:21:45,219
Jiajia, eat some meat.

363
00:21:45,219 --> 00:21:49,240
No, let me tell you. This Niu Wanwan is tutoring Dong Dawei.

364
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:54,732
- That Dong Dawei just follows behind Niu Wanwan all the time like a minion.
- Wow.

365
00:21:54,732 --> 00:21:59,880
Once, Niu Wanwan just tossed a scratch paper.

366
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:03,300
- Dong Dawei picked it up and kept it until now.
- Oh, God.

367
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:08,239
The most important thing is, Niu Wanwan doesn't even know his name.

368
00:22:09,060 --> 00:22:12,900
Bro, can you tolerate that?

369
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:16,366
Let's order him something hard-core.

370
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:27,640
This is… Who ordered this?

371
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:31,239
- Table 1's customer ordered it for Brother Gao.
- Wow!

372
00:22:31,239 --> 00:22:33,380
Brother Gao!

373
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:38,040
No, no. Don't mock me.

374
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:44,819
Well, I, Gao Yang... How do I put it? I have a certain status in Tieyuan.

375
00:22:44,819 --> 00:22:48,100
Go ahead and eat first. I'll go social with them for a bit.

376
00:22:49,739 --> 00:22:51,487
- I'll get some for you.
- Thank you.

377
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:53,901
Eat some more.

378
00:22:55,499 --> 00:22:57,780
Gao Yang has such a status here?

379
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:58,939
He doesn't.

380
00:22:58,939 --> 00:23:01,419
He's not trying to skip the bill, is he?

381
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:06,200
Who cares about him? Let's hurry and eat.

382
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:20,639
Come on. Repeat what you said over there to me again.

383
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:23,819
I just said…

384
00:23:23,819 --> 00:23:29,040
I said you're... a dragon (outstanding) amongst the people. Yes.

385
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:33,279
You love to study and you're...

386
00:23:33,279 --> 00:23:38,940
a perfect match with Sister Wanwan. You're perfect for each other. That's right.

387
00:23:44,060 --> 00:23:49,500
Well, my friends are still waiting for me to pay the bill. I'll also pay your bill while I'm at it.

388
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:51,520
I'm leaving now.

389
00:23:52,520 --> 00:23:55,919
Did I say you can leave? Did I say you can leave?

390
00:23:55,919 --> 00:24:00,130
Dong Dawei, you're a student too.

391
00:24:00,130 --> 00:24:03,363
If you cause trouble, none of us can go to school.

392
00:24:03,363 --> 00:24:07,119
I don't care what beef you have with Mr. Gao. It has nothing to do with Gao Yang.

393
00:24:07,119 --> 00:24:09,639
Who are you?

394
00:24:09,639 --> 00:24:11,694
I'm Ye Xiaowen.

395
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:31,755
Gao Yang, let's go.

396
00:24:47,359 --> 00:24:51,760
Brother Dawei, enjoy your food. Well, study hard when you go back.

397
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,319
Did I say you can leave?

398
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:03,240
Move the chair away.

399
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,900
What if I don't?

400
00:25:05,900 --> 00:25:09,119
My mom bought these for me. Move it away.

401
00:25:13,639 --> 00:25:15,700
You have a mom?

402
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:20,540
Your mom left you. Your dad doesn't care about you.

403
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:23,340
You're just something that no one wants.

404
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:33,459
Who are you saying doesn't have parents?

405
00:26:10,780 --> 00:26:12,505
Brother Bin,

406
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:15,430
you're a good person.

407
00:26:16,140 --> 00:26:19,000
You raised the child all alone.

408
00:26:19,540 --> 00:26:21,832
It really wasn't easy for you.

409
00:26:26,300 --> 00:26:28,300
Here's a toast to you.

410
00:26:48,699 --> 00:26:51,399
What's so great about Anna?

411
00:26:53,419 --> 00:26:56,680
All she knows is how to use her stinking money.

412
00:26:58,079 --> 00:27:02,179
Is that considered love? Does she love Gao Yang?

413
00:27:05,760 --> 00:27:07,475
Fine,

414
00:27:09,930 --> 00:27:12,839
Let me see what your love is like.

415
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:20,460
A game console,

416
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:25,783
international brand-name clothing,

417
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:30,183
they are pretty expensive.

418
00:27:33,490 --> 00:27:35,531
Pretty expensive indeed.

419
00:27:37,459 --> 00:27:39,680
I can't afford them.

420
00:28:14,150 --> 00:28:16,920
Why am I such a loser?

421
00:28:22,079 --> 00:28:25,340
What kind of father am I?

422
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:30,499
That's enough.

423
00:28:34,839 --> 00:28:37,200
Look at you.

424
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:39,973
Don't bring shame to us Northeastern men, all right?

425
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:46,394
Boss,

426
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:48,499
come and have a few drinks.

427
00:28:48,499 --> 00:28:50,750
You should stop.

428
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:54,960
Think about it. If your child sees you like this, what would he think?

429
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:43,771
Hey,

430
00:29:44,879 --> 00:29:46,782
Gao Yang?

431
00:29:46,782 --> 00:29:48,432
Are you asleep?

432
00:29:48,432 --> 00:29:50,646
Out with it.

433
00:29:53,979 --> 00:29:58,660
Do you think Dong Dawei would tell the teachers about Mi Jia?

434
00:29:58,660 --> 00:29:59,960
Don't worry.

435
00:30:00,739 --> 00:30:03,499
When he sees the teachers, he walks the other way.

436
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:09,513
Let me tell you something.

437
00:30:12,979 --> 00:30:15,559
That Mi Jia is pretty fierce.

438
00:30:15,559 --> 00:30:18,980
She even dares to smack Dong Dawei. I like that.

439
00:30:18,980 --> 00:30:20,900
Would Beibei tell the principal?

440
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:22,562
Don't worry.

441
00:30:22,562 --> 00:30:26,380
We are the closest friends. She won't rat us out.

442
00:30:26,380 --> 00:30:29,859
Just take care of yourself. I will look after Mi Jia.

443
00:30:30,659 --> 00:30:34,960
However, that Dong Dawei is already onto us.

444
00:30:37,860 --> 00:30:41,019
What beef do you have with Dong Dawei anyway?

445
00:30:41,699 --> 00:30:43,700
It's Gao Bin's fault.

446
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:48,040
He recruited Dong Dawei to the soccer team as the goalie back then.

447
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:51,659
After that, he dismissed Dong Dawei for fighting.

448
00:30:51,659 --> 00:30:54,679
After that, he comes to me looking for trouble every day.

449
00:30:54,679 --> 00:30:57,419
Don't be fooled thinking Gao Bin is like a teacher.

450
00:30:57,419 --> 00:30:59,320
He caused a lot of trouble.

451
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:04,219
If it wasn't for me, he wouldn't be able to survive in Tieyuan.

452
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:08,219
By the way, you can't tell him about this.

453
00:31:08,219 --> 00:31:10,750
If he finds out, it will just get messier.

454
00:31:12,979 --> 00:31:14,532
Go to sleep.

455
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:24,520
Does Mi Jia have a little stutter?

456
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:28,539
She did when she was a child. It's much better now.

457
00:31:28,539 --> 00:31:32,440
If she doesn't get very emotional, we can hardly hear it.

458
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:34,860
Hey, don't tell anyone.

459
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:36,538
Don't worry.

460
00:31:37,459 --> 00:31:39,140
But is she a congenital stutterer or an acquired stutterer?

461
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:40,300
Are you asking for a beating?

462
00:31:40,300 --> 00:31:44,719
I'm just concerned for our schoolmates. Otherwise, how will I watch over her in school?

463
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:51,759
But Mi Jia

464
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:53,700
surely looks pretty.

465
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:55,557
It's just…

466
00:31:56,140 --> 00:31:58,559
It's just her personality...

467
00:31:58,559 --> 00:32:02,100
Why is it fiercer than Beibei's? No, that won't do.

468
00:32:02,100 --> 00:32:04,209
Stay away from her.

469
00:32:06,839 --> 00:32:09,031
I'll stay away from her.

470
00:32:10,979 --> 00:32:15,260
If she's willing, I can accept her reluctantly.

471
00:32:17,179 --> 00:32:20,300
Go to sleep. I'm just kidding. Let's go to sleep.

472
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:22,100
Really.

473
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:24,836
I won't mess around anymore. I know you can fight.

474
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:42,100
It'll be perfect if Mi Jia is more cold and reserved.

475
00:32:42,100 --> 00:32:43,679
Turn off the light.

476
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:54,260
Bro, are you okay? Does it still hurt?

477
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:03,779
Brother Dawei, I've found out!

478
00:33:03,779 --> 00:33:07,140
That little girl is a Sophomore.

479
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:11,580
- Let's go to school tomorrow and bring her here.
- If I hit a girl, can I still keep my reputation?

480
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:13,580
You can't let a girl beat you either.

481
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:17,120
Lower your voice. Don't let Brother Dawei's dad hear us.

482
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:21,459
Then are we just going to let it go like that?

483
00:33:21,459 --> 00:33:23,507
No way.

484
00:33:23,507 --> 00:33:29,140
I will settle both old and new scores once and for all with Gao Yang.

485
00:33:51,990 --> 00:33:58,030
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

486
00:33:58,030 --> 00:34:05,300
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

487
00:34:05,300 --> 00:34:11,290
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

488
00:34:11,290 --> 00:34:17,430
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

489
00:34:17,430 --> 00:34:23,980
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

490
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:29,620
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

491
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:33,510
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

492
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:36,950
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

493
00:34:36,950 --> 00:34:40,250
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

494
00:34:40,250 --> 00:34:47,010
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

495
00:34:47,010 --> 00:34:50,220
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

496
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:54,430
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

497
00:34:54,430 --> 00:34:58,250
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

498
00:34:58,250 --> 00:35:05,110
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
